data.text: @ScottMendelson @Forbes After the highly disappointing John Wick 2 and this casting update I will now be lowering my expectations for John Wick 3 a great deal. Hopefully they will surprise me with a great film, but I am not holding my breath.
@ScottMendelson @Forbes I think Ruby Rose's character died if you factor in what Wick said to Common. By that, Common should be coming back.
